     * Contacts

Copenhagen

     * Overview
     * Our Team
     * Culture
     * Carrières
     * Social Impact
     * Recent Insights
     * Contacts

     *
     *

   Since our office was established in 2007, Bain Copenhagen has been
   consistently recognized as one of the top strategy consulting partners
   for both national and global firms across Denmark. Our team primarily
   serves Danish companies across the Nordics and worldwide, with a
   particular emphasis on locally relevant private equity and financial
   investors. Our office is part of Bain Nordic, which works together with
   the Helsinki, Oslo and Stockholm offices.

   We continually strive to sustain high client and employee loyalty. Our
   greatest promoters are clients and former employees who have
   experienced an outstanding depth of results.

Our Team

