   Bain Doha operates in conjunction with our Abu Dhabi, Beirut, Dubai,
   and Riyadh offices as Bain Middle East. Through the Doha office, Bain
   serves clients across a broad range of sectors spanning both the public
   and private domains, with the goal of helping make a lasting impact on
   both businesses and society at large.

